三种方案，按场景选：

**方案一：@JsonIgnoreProperties + JOIN FETCH（推荐）**

```java
@Entity
public class User {
    @OneToMany(mappedBy = "user", fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
    @JsonIgnoreProperties("user")  // 防止循环引用
    private List<Order> orders;
}

// Repository 中显式 fetch
@Query("SELECT u FROM User u JOIN FETCH u.orders WHERE u.id = :id")
Optional<User> findByIdWithOrders(@Param("id") Long id);
```

**方案二：DTO 投影（生产推荐）**

```java
// 不返回 Entity，返回专用 DTO
public record UserDTO(Long id, String name, List<OrderDTO> orders) {}
public record OrderDTO(Long id, BigDecimal amount) {}

@Query("SELECT new com.example.dto.UserDTO(u.id, u.name) FROM User u WHERE u.id = :id")
